title: Snakes On A Plane - New Line Platinum Series Widescreen (MKV)
description:
R | 1h 45min | Action, Adventure | August 18th 2006




An FBI agent takes on a plane full of deadly and venomous snakes, deliberately released to kill a witness being flown from Honolulu to Los Angeles to testify against a mob boss.




Director: David R. Ellis

Writers: John Heffernan (screenplay), Sebastian Gutierrez (screenplay)

Stars: Samuel L. Jackson, Julianna Margulies, Nathan Phillips 


Extras Include: Blooper Reel, Deleted Scenes, Pure Venom-The Making Of Snakes On A Plane and more.

Feature commentary by Samuel L. Jackson, David R. Ellis and more.

English Audio and English & Spanish Subtitles
